title: New River Studios Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A cafe at the front part of a studio complex in an industrial building where regular music gigs take place. Offers tea, coffee, soft drinks, alcohol, vegan snacks like quiche and cookies. Has soymilk for drinks. Open space with old sofas and tables.
